		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2"><a name="1108509103184459006"></a><span class="msgSubject">Timing Healing spells</span><br clear="all" /><script type="text/javascript">document.title = document.title + ": Thread: Timing Healing spells";</script>
		   <span class="sm">Posted: Feb 15th  2005 at  7:12pm EDT<span class="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a class="sm" href="/db/classes.html?class=7;mid=1108509103184459006;num=4;page=1;post=1;replyto=1108509103184459006"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a>    </span></span></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" class="mform" ><span class="fs8"><span class="notbold">By: </span><a href="/db/poster.html?user=512244"><span class="">Ikeeluu</span></a><b><span class=""></span></b><br />4 posts
